div.div:
A medical camp is conducted every first sunday of the month. A patient has certain details like name, phone_no, camp_id, consultation_history (which contains the list of previous doctor visits from the camp), sex, height, weight, etc. The patient needs to go through certain steps before each consultation. 1. register and get the token. 2. general consultation where height and general stats are collected. 3.doctor consultation. 4. prescribed checkup (eye check up, thyroid checkup etc) 5. give samples for tests. 6. get prescribed drugs and medical aids. No fee is collected from the patient since its being sponsored for the under privelaged sector.
We cannot use contact_no as an identifier, since there are cases where one contact_no is used for every member in the family.Â
A patient can consult one or more doctors.
A doctor can prescribe one or more of tests, midication, check ups
A patient can have 0 or many reports from the tests
Inventory conatins all the details of the midication, optical aids prescribed
